          "text": "Hypotension\n,\nsyncope\nExtrapyramidal symptoms:\ntardive dyskinesia\nNeuroleptic malignant syndrome\n,\nhyperthermia\nHyperglycemia\n,\ndiabetes mellitus\n,\nDKA\nSeizure\n,\nPriapism\n,\nStroke\n,\nTIA\nDysphagia\nLeukopenia\n,\nNeutropenia\n,\nAgranulocytosis\nSuicidality\nPancreatitis",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Common": {
          "text": "Akathisia, dystonia, parkinsonism, tremor\nSedation/\nfatigue\n,\ndizziness\n, blurred vision,\nanxiety\n, confusion\nRash\nHyperprolactinemia, weight gain, increased appetite\nConstipation\n,\ndiarrhea\n,\nnausea\n/\nvomiting\nUrinary incontinence\nCough\n, URI\nPhotosensitivity\n, visual disturbance",
          "tables": []
